{{Top|leg}}
'''Rotting disease''' was a type of disease that was propagated by the [[tesfli piercer]], which were native to the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Gorsh]]. Victims bitten by the tesfli piercer who did not seek medical attention found the bitten [[Limb/Legends|limb]] suddenly swollen and then turn a [[Color/Legends|discolored]] black. The flesh soon fell apart, rendering the limb useless. This disease was at its worst when a victim was bitten dozens or hundreds of [[Time/Legends|times]] upon encountering a swarm of these [[Insect/Legends|insects]].

